Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  傷到頭髮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼非要進行這種訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日米共同計畫的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本和柯美利亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為國際月球空間站的建設終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國際月球空間站？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
