Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是乖乖地躺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你們3人的身體都沒什麼異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A小隊報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的女性超能力者一名  迄今仍沒有抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B小隊也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C小隊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白  皆本為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯美利亞大使館發來回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛琳大尉在宇宙中心毫無問題地從事著計畫內容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來柯美利亞是有事情想瞞著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明在他身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過居然能把LV7你們修理成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人是怎樣的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木醫生  你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那個人果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制器處於解禁狀態哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話了  「果然是」是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在柯美利亞時代有過女人吧  ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我誠實招來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個叫凱莉的女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說凱莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是這麼說的嗎  小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果知道些什麼的話  就告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事  賢木君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是卡洛琳•瑪姬大尉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情要追溯到在柯美利亞留學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔  醫生你和皆本先生應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊的大學成為朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢…賢木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我賢木就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是結束了大部分必修科目準備回國的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本  皆本  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿梅利亞  翁莉  茱蒂  克莉絲還有庫夏娜都會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群一看就別有用心的多國籍成員是搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  這可是最後的聯誼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是未成年啊  沒法像你一樣放開手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得那麼死板嘛  這裡是柯美利亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情都是個人的自由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來努力改變日本人羞澀的印象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全改成你這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊  既然好不容易身為男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  站在路中間是很危險的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然作為賠禮  今晚我來陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  修二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  你嘴上雖然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但心裡其實是在想著邀請女生的計畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來已經傳遍校內了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那一點不都羞澀的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是皆本光一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也是日本人  不過請不要把我和他混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照  我是卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今晚到底怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我接下來要去幫沃倫斯教授
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫教授？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  你應該是LV2的念動能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是修二  女生的資料全都掌握在手中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要敷衍我  卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你莫非是那個實驗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是亂說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是找教授商量畢業後的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出路？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將來想到宇宙上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我從小的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木  那個實驗是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是個傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說ESP研究家的沃倫斯教授對低LV的超能力者的大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施加外在的刺激來強行提升LV
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ESP實驗樓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在知道風險的情況下同意實驗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用畢業後的出路為餌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還虧你們是教育機關啊  沃倫斯教授
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  她到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像個嬰兒一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗的結果  她成為了高LV超能力者  並且是複合能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是記憶和人格全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼事情會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下可棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是超能力中樞開始新活動的時候產生了新的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那卡洛琳已經？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是皆本君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她非常黏你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…  沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本  簡直就是為了照顧小孩而出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  為了能讓她恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能來幫我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有恢復方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能將兩個人格合二為一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是將腦的機能統一的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的人格就會和以前的人格合併
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…那樣的話即使不是我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我們是辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎很不喜歡我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前幾天的爆炸就是因為這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  我們不想大學再遭破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣很痛的  能住手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡羅…磷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  她連自己的名字也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡羅麗麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉  凱莉  凱凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時就叫凱莉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  我會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是有條件的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再發生這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你們能夠終止高LV超能力者的開發實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙絕對很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対アイツでかいって{
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯美利亞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,コメリカだもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中村悠一くんは暑がりよね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川悠一君很怕熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  不過光一不會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  還是忘記他比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本其實對成熟女性沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便散播無根無據的流言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  光一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒童向的書？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給凱莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有在做看護小孩的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是他家的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這樣很好玩嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來玩吧 玩吧 玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  今天不是約好給你念書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要念書  我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲避球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  用那個球？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這麼玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  這沒法一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們會死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先看書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了統一你的大腦機能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最快的方法是發展語言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我變聰明了   凱莉就會消失對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是和本來的人格相統一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說只是恢復原樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念力會留下來  也應該不會忘記現在在這裡做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就不是凱莉了  凱莉會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉不想消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類是會成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而成長就意味著改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說成長是很緩慢的所以無法察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實我們每天都在扮演著不同的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是內心還是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果你一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那卡洛琳要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一喜歡卡洛琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起凱莉來要更喜歡卡洛琳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭凱莉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要為難皆本  凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是想讓你成為大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了大家著想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我成為大人之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我更加成熟之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  這要等到那個時候才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那凱莉會長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長大之後  光一一定會喜歡上凱莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你就不會再讓我變回卡洛琳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情算是有眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是過了一段時間後皆本先生就和她交往了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生太齷齪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和自己照顧的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都不對我們下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 很不公平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不二子有點對皆本君另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要自己一個人在那找樂子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管理官…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉的精神發展追上肉體的速度比我們預想中的要快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  那是過了一個月左右的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒過來了嗎  光一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…凱莉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的  是凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我能看懂德語了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是法語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過感覺不是我自己記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是卡洛琳的知識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候會回想起我不知道的人或場所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就要消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過好多次了  你並不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變化了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對我來說你就是全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為愛著光一的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變回卡洛琳的話  就沒法像這樣愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為和我不同  除了你以外她還有著其他的過去和回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她也應該會喜歡光一的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對她來說  自己去宇宙的夢想才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我和卡洛琳是無法融合的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是不想融合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓這份感情只屬於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後能給我個回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候凱莉以自己的意志封印了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入了沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  你為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我好想見你啊  光一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉的記憶並沒有完全恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是哪個超能力者覺醒了  跑過來一看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果又是和那小子有關的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局長  D小隊發來緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是常盤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現皆本二尉和卡洛琳大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這意識不是卡洛琳而是凱莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之皆本先生平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  這裡是局長室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管理官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生  我是野分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請待在那裡不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡森大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒打算加害你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說  柯美利亞重新開始了高LV超能力者的開發實驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細情況乃機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是關係到國家利益的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本政府也同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怪我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要用槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是軍人  所以無法違抗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是朋友  但是絕不會讓你們阻攔我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的東西是ME的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ME的東西是ME的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有這種單方面的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬移嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制器…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了  {\i1}The Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總理剛剛來電
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說將這件事全權交給柯美利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝協助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆  為什麼來礙事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介入這件事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:22:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是你們也會被以違反國際法定罪並逮捕的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…我們？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不付諸於實力你們是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳做什麼啊？  老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老奶奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的絕對可憐{\i1}The Children{\i} 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽我說  凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉無論如何都想看一下光一出生的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:24:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果皆本先生選擇了凱莉的話…
